Use the standard library
This is how to f of n:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 1
  Remember that fact is 1
  Do this n times:
    When remainder of i and 5 is 0, then:
      Add result to i
    But, if not:
      Remember that fact is product of fact and i
      Add result to fact
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
